    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen. but nothing happens. i just wake up and feel this void, and every single day is just more of the same emptiness. i'm just so tired of fighting to exist in a world that feels completely empty of everything i loved. why am i even trying to keep going through this? it feels like the pain is the only thing that's actually real anymore.",
